Color in life (
Fig. 4
). Dorsum light brown with black irregular blotches bordered by light brown edges. Dorsal and lateral tubercles at the edge of the blotches yellow to white. Head brown with dark brown blotches, a U-shaped dark brown nuchal band is continuous from eye to eye. Eyelids yellowish brown to yellow. Iris brown with black vertical pupil. Labial scale series covered in yellow blotches. Original tail creamy-white with 10 black transverse bands.
